  "text": "Expanding upon the work of Lukas et al. [CITATION_1] , our experiments report high accuracy results. The next step of this work is tuning the classification model for one class classification, in which we train the classifier with a given class of interest only. This can be useful in an Open Set scenario, when we have access to only one camera.",
